  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a retrospective research in order to compare and analysis the risk factor,
      clinical manifestation and efficacy of albicans candidemia by pulling medical records. We
      hope that this retrospective research will let us understand the method of treatment and
      prevention of albicans candidemia in order to improve the quality of healthcare.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
